headline: Schwab Expands Support of RIATA Student Scholarship as It Celebrates Five Years; University Grant Program Set to Reach $25M Milestone in 2025
summary: WESTLAKE, Texas, November 20, 2024--Today, Schwab Advisor Services™ in partnership with Charles Schwab Foundation announced the expansion of its Registered Investment Advisor Talent Advantage (RIATA) Student Scholarship program. In celebration of its fifth anniversary in 2025, the scholarship program will now award $15,000 to 15 students toward their academic enrollment, increasing the number of students to 15 and amount received by $5,000.
